sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client
    participant AGW as Agentgateway Proxy
    participant STS as Token Exchange Server (STS)
    participant UI as Solo Enterprise UI
    participant OAuth as External OAuth Provider
    participant API as Upstream API

    Client->>AGW: Request (needs upstream OAuth token)
    AGW->>STS: Request upstream token
    STS->>AGW: Return elicitation URL (PENDING)
    AGW->>Client: Return elicitation URL (PENDING)
    Client->>UI: Open the elicitation URL and authorize
    UI->>OAuth: Redirect for OAuth authorization
    OAuth->>UI: Redirect back with authorization code
    UI->>STS: Complete elicitation with authorization code
    STS->>STS: Store token, update elicitation (COMPLETED)
    Client->>AGW: Retry request
    AGW->>STS: Fetch stored token
    STS->>AGW: Return stored token
    AGW->>API: Forward request and inject stored OAuth token
    API-->>AGW: Response
    AGW-->>Client: Result
